        {
            "title": "油尖打擊違泊發逾千張牛肉乾  非華裔漢涉無牌駕駛電單車被捕",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"警方圖片\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/4e16324accfecbfb343ddf5c564cf516/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250510/_2025051007220332436.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">警方圖片</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>油尖警區聯同西九龍總區交通部人員昨日（9日）在區內進行代號「動天」（MOVESKY）的打擊區內違例泊車黑點行動。<br/>\n<br/>\n行動期間，人員共發出一千○五十九張定額罰款通知書及拖走十輛對交通造成嚴重阻塞的車輛，並拘捕一名49歲非華裔男子，他涉嫌「駕駛時沒有有效駕駛執照」、「駕駛未有登記的車輛」、「駕駛時沒有第三者保險」及「駕駛電單車時沒有戴上認可防護頭盔」。<br/>\n<br/>\n該名被捕男子已獲准保釋候查，須於六月上旬向警方報到。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4240424/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/03358c55099f3940c6c53e8ff8913fdb/2025-05/MIU_MOVESKY_ADOO_YTDIST_1.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p><br/>\n截至二○二五年四月，油尖警區共發出七萬九千三百九十九張定額罰款通知書及攝錄到五百○三宗司機違例事項，希望駕駛者藉此改善可能引致交通意外的不良行為。<br/>\n<br/>\n油尖警區將持續嚴厲執法，確保交通暢通及提高道路使用者的道路安全與守法意識，以保障市民安全。警方呼籲駕駛人士遵守交通規則，切勿因一時之便違例停泊車輛。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2068195/即時-港聞-油尖打擊違泊發逾千張牛肉乾-非華裔漢涉無牌駕駛電單車被捕",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-10 07:31:56",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "天文台｜最高氣溫約29度 稍後及今晚驟雨逐漸增多 部分地區雨勢較大",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/ca88ff917b78ba05e486f899537e04b8/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250510/_2025051007100493529.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">蔡楚輝攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>廣東沿岸風勢微弱。同時，華中的氣壓正在上升，預料一道冷鋒今日會在華南北部形成，並在今晚橫過沿岸地區。\n\n</p>\n<p>本港地區今日大致多雲，有幾陣驟雨。早上部分時間天色明朗。最高氣溫約29度。日間稍後及今晚驟雨逐漸增多及有幾陣狂風雷暴，部分地區雨勢較大。吹微風，晚上北風增強，氣溫逐步下降至午夜最低約23度。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4240416/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"日間稍後及今晚驟雨逐漸增多及有幾陣狂風雷暴，部分地區雨勢較大。蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cbdf6683e2da040e5778f60ed12325df/2025-05/4_0_1.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        日間稍後及今晚驟雨逐漸增多及有幾陣狂風雷暴，部分地區雨勢較大。蔡楚輝攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4240417/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5cda3c7631a664692009367f76422def/2025-05/Screenshot_2025-05-10_at_12_03_35_AM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"me